ygData.messageBody:
Prepair for death if you plan on entering Troll town, don't think they like barbarians

>>> "Patricia Halas" <patty_halas@...> 5.17.99 2:04:27 PM >>>
From: "Patricia Halas" <patty_halas@...>

I am going back to North Ro now that I have finally reached the 12th Rank
of Barbarian Warrior. Hopefully soon I will have enougth plat to afford my
dream weapon of a combine long sword (I have 10 plat now).
Any good suggestions for hunting in and around Freeport? Didn't like
befallen to much since I don't have a magic weapon yet. Kind of a bummer
when you have to run from a skel that cons blue since I can't hit him.
Haven't been down to see Troll Town yet. Wonder if it is worth the trip?

For the Honor and Glory of Rellos Zek;

Patty of Halas
